inductive Ordering where
  | Less : Ordering
  | Equal : Ordering
  | Greater : Ordering
  structure Ord (Self : Type) where
    cmp : Self → Self → Result Ordering
  inductive Node (T : Type) where
  | mk : T → Option (Node T) → Option (Node T) → Isize → Node T
  @[reducible]
  def Node.value {T : Type}
